              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="voice-duration">0:32</span>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-3); font-style: italic;">
            "Let's start by just... slowing down. Take a breath with me. In through your nose...
            and out through your mouth. Good. The day is done. You've done enough. Now it's time to rest."
